    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense for a general overview, but for my paper I really need to get into the specifics of their \"evidence.\" Can you give some more detailed examples of the actual \"scientific\" claims they made regarding different racial groups? Like, how did they specifically rank them or what kind of metrics were they using to prove one group was \"superior\" to another?",
